{"tid":1506384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長矛兵應該要係點嘅樣！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-25T19:06:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T03:21:55.000Z","uid":3722,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"0958a4fbd8cff407f4976e8d9206f57b200cf8f8","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:06:04.000Z","msg":"見唔少玩家玩香城ＯＮＬＩＮＥ都想有戰術，有組織咁玩。<br />\n咁小妹就想畀個建議出嚟，講下如果起方陣嘅話，第一排嘅玩家應該點著裝。<br />\n都係嗰句，呢個ｐｏｓｔ只不過係小妹玩香城ＯＮＬＩＮＥ同睇書上網整合出嚟嘅一啲建議，<br />\n大家可以喺下面一齊討論。<br />\n有興趣睇下小妹提出嘅戰術嘅玩家可以㩒下面呢條link <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">［重開］［整合］香城Online 職業整合與戰術討論<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1503154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1503154</a></span><br />\n<br />\n1. 安全，後面嘅人可以捉住前面嘅人嘅皮帶，再後面嘅人又可以捉住前面嘅人嘅皮帶。<br />\n一兩個人就好易畀怪捉走，但係三四個人就難了。<br />\n2. 減少對個人能力嘅要求，唔使做到葉問咁先至打到怪。<br />\n3. 用啱裝備嘅話，防禦能力大大提升，類似協同效應嘅原理。<br />\n<br />\n然後方陣嘅第一排就會係長矛兵。<br />\n長矛兵有分兩隻，一種係雙手矛兵，例子有日本戰國嘅足輕同埋長矛武士，又或者馬其頓嘅超長矛兵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qMYYFV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qMYYFV.jpg&h=5659a287&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YAJTNzo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYAJTNzo.jpg&h=42fef553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 雙手矛兵嘅好處係易訓練，啫係難度唔高，只要夠多人，唔係習武之人都可以有效壓迫敵人。<br />\n- 而且雙手持矛攻擊力高，對敵方嘅近戰步兵<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（fong4 bou6）</span>同騎兵<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（cuk1 lung4）</span>都可以做到壓倒性嘅守勢。<br />\n- 但係唔好處係佢哋對遠程火力可以話係零防禦力，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">面積細嘅矛就算幾密集都無法媲美盾牌嘅防禦力。</span></strong>（馬其頓方陣嚟講，佢哋個盾對比起枝矛實在係太細，攞住咁長嘅矛，根本冇辦法再舉盾抵擋由上而下嘅箭雨）<br />\n<br />\n另一種就係矛盾兵，一手持矛一手持盾。例子有希臘同羅馬嘅Hoplite。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/byAbzeU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbyAbzeU.jpg&h=4c4b714e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 矛盾兵嘅盾同矛比例合理，即使要砌長矛陣都唔係難事。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rLCpUjF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrLCpUjF.jpg&h=b9d551cf&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n- 遠程火力唔再係致命傷，就算係直射嘅火力<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">（zoeng6 gaau1 daan2）</span>都可以輕易抵擋。<br />\n- 因為枝矛唔係長到痴線，單手都可以操縱自如。好似上圖咁嘅陣式就可以令到<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">士兵一方面有足夠防禦力</span></strong>，另一方面可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對鳩衝嘅敵方近戰兵造成傷害。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n所以我認為矛盾兵比起雙手矛兵會係一個更加平衡嘅職業，打怪之餘又有足夠保護措施。"},{"pid":"7b5a8119c232518e36972150c992eac1bfe840b8","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:06:07.000Z","msg":"講返香城ＯＮＬＩＮＥ，咁喺呢個前提之下，玩家應該點著裝呢？<br />\n我就改咗以下呢張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Uct8BAL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUct8BAL.png&h=a0c3a80f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n最重要嘅兩點就係<br />\n1. 矛：買枝cheap 雞行山杖，但係要留意返尖端位嘅形狀，膠的係唔會造到傷害，連趕走啲怪都做唔到㗎。<br />\n2. 盾，<span style=\"color: red;\">愈大愈好</span>，因為一嚟擋到棍撃嘅面積大啲，二嚟就係當怪獸開遠技嘅時候，玩家可以蹲低到同個盾一樣嘅高度，<span style=\"color: red;\">將怪獸嘅直接命中率減至零</span>。<br />\n裝甲方面，因為㨂呢個職業嘅玩家係最前線，所以玩家自己衡量經濟，靈活度，同性命嘅比重啦。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">防具 口罩  圖鑑&amp; 購買連結   保護自已 保護他人<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit#gid=1972697016\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4%2Fedit%23gid%3D1972697016&d=yer2B7JdR0FeQcPip%2BSHxpktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=33818ae5\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1X_p56W1VLpfWTqdVb3-C8wlLMzfcy8qH6h8w41VTyu4/edit#gid=1972697016</a></span><br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">以上以下純屬學術研究交流。<br />\n只供遊戲用途，並不誘使或鼓吹任何行動。<br />\n若使用本頁資訊導致任何（法律）問題，本頁及相關人士恕不負責。</span>"},{"pid":"2eed271504993576209ad1e707591c7865213be4","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:07:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38bdfe424f8a01c00a6f36799446361a9145b74d","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:07:20.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"4e769992dae0fc0d470b145fabc57f9ba182b6fa","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:08:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74af26b980db534fb538829596d7589ce4e89256","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:08:39.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"c74ef5ddea600539af14e788424d351d775c458a","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:09:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e86c6faec45282ab6c3df39a4731054bce07bf47","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:09:45.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"49b53e66872b3922e5f10fe639085b0bc1ac8dea","tid":1506384,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:10:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810e452e5cc652c51479bc8c90e1aa85f93aefc9","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:10:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4bd34f27c727ff0ac0550e072cd54594295f63bc","tid":1506384,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:10:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b14528750a920cb3640170f456cada7916952793","tid":1506384,"uid":3722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:10:29.000Z","msg":"拉"},{"pid":"5d766b0856c984e1d31a78ba50ae9a5969a4911b","tid":1506384,"uid":219277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T19:10:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/face